Build fedora sdcard image for rockpi4b:

cd ~/Downloads
wget https://archives.fedoraproject.org/pub/fedora/linux/releases/43/Workstation/aarch64/images/Fedora-Workstation-Disk-43-1.6.aarch64.raw.xz

Plugin USB3 1TB SSD to PC. 
sudo ./mksdcardimg.sh
sudo mkfs.vfat /dev/sda1
sudo mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda2
sudo mkfs.ext4 /dev/sda3
sudo fdisk -l /dev/sda
xzcat ~/Downloads/Fedora-Workstation-Disk-43-1.6.aarch64.raw.xz | sudo dd status=progress bs=4096 of=/dev/sda skip=4352 seek=4352 conv=notrunc,fsync
Eject USB3 1TB SSD from PC.

Plugin USB3 1TB SSD and ethernet cable to rockpi4b. Power on rockpi4b.

Disable power saving and screen saver.

sudo btrfs filesystem resize max /
df .
uname -a
cat /etc/fedora-release
sudo systemctl start sshd.service
sudo systemctl enable sshd.service
sudo ifconfig
rpm -qa | grep -i kernel
sudo dnf install kernel-devel-6.17.1-300.fc43.aarch64
rpm -qa | grep -i kernel
add: exclude=kernel* to /etc/dnf/dnf.conf
sudo dnf update
sudo grub2-editenv create
sudo grub2-mkconfig -o /boot/grub2/grub.cfg
sudo sudo grubby --set-default /boot/vmlinuz-6.17.1-300.fc43.aarch64
sudo grubby --default-kernel
sudo grubby --info DEFAULT
sudo grubby --info /boot/vmlinuz-6.17.1-300.fc43.aarch64
sudo ls -l /boot/loader/entries
sync
free
sudo shutdown -h now

Plugin USB3 1TB SSD to PC.
sudo mount /dev/sda3 /mnt
sudo cp ./packages/* /mnt/root/lib/firmware/brcm/
sync; sudo umount /mnt;
Eject USB3 1TB SSD from PC.

Plugin USB3 1TB SSD to rockpi4b. Remove ethernet cable. Power on rockpi4b.
Setup wifi.
uname -a
cat /etc/fedora-release
sudo dnf install speedtest-cli glmark2-es2-wayland mpv yt-dlp pavucontrol openssl-devel vsftpd vlc pandoc vsftpd

speedtest-cli --secure
glmark2-es2-wayland

aplay -l
pavucontrol  ( select hdmi as default )

sudo vi /etc/vsftpd/vsftpd.conf
sudo systemctl restart vsftpd
sudo firewall-cmd --add-service=ftp --permanent
sudo firewall-cmd --reload
sudo firewall-cmd --list-all

Do follows on PC, then ftp swan.mp4 to rockpi4b
(
git clone https://github.com/yt-dlp/yt-dlp.git
cd yt-dlp
make 
cd ../
~/yt-dlp/yt-dlp -f 'bestvideo[ext=mp4][protocol=https]+bestaudio[ext=m4a][protocol=https]' 3qrKjywjo7Q -o swan.mp4 --postprocessor-args " -vf scale=1280:720 -r 10 -c:v libx264 -b:v 2M -c:a copy"
)

mpv --hwdec=auto-copy swan.mp4
ffplay swan.mp4
cvlc --gl=wgl --glconv=any swan.mp4

sudo rfkill list
bluetoothctl
scan on -> scan off -> exit
